<h2>The Safe Way to Build Do-Follow Backlinks</h2>
<p>Building dofollow backlinks requires discipline. Google penalizes manipulative link patterns. Here is how to build backlinks that improve your rankings without triggering penalties.</p>
<h3>Maintain a Natural Link Profile</h3>
<p>A natural backlink profile has a mix of dofollow and nofollow links. The optimal ratio is 70:30 or 60:40 dofollow to nofollow. If 100% of your backlinks are dofollow, Google flags that as unnatural.</p>
<p>Search Engine Land has 82.2% followed referring domains. That ratio is considered healthy and organic.</p>
