<h3>Build Links Gradually</h3>
<p>No more than 15 to 20 new backlinks per day. Sudden spikes in link acquisition trigger spam detection. Consistent, gradual growth over months is the safest approach.</p>
<h3>Prioritize Relevance Over DA</h3>
<p>A link from a smaller niche blog in your industry outperforms a generic high-DA site. Google weighs topical relevance in 2026 more than ever. A DA 45 marketing blog linking to your marketing content beats a DA 90 cooking site.</p>
