<p>Use Google Search Console, Ahrefs, or Semrush to track your backlinks monthly. Watch for <a href="/blog/toxic-backlinks-guide/">toxic backlinks</a> that could trigger a penalty. Disavow any spammy or harmful links promptly.</p>
